03:45.934 --> 03:47.060
Yeah.

03:47.978 --> 03:49.604
- Did you talk to him?
- Not yet.

03:49.688 --> 03:52.524
- Would you talk to him?
- Talk to me about what?

03:56.486 --> 03:58.280
Talk to me about what?

04:00.323 --> 04:02.492
